==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Divisional
<hw>Di*vi"sion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>That divides;
pertaining to, making, or noting, a division; <as>as, a
<ex>divisional</ex> line; a <ex>divisional</ex> general; a
<ex>divisional</ex> surgeon of police.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Divisional planes</b></col> <fld>(Geol.)</fld>,
<cd>planes of separation between rock masses. They include
joints.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Divisionally</ent>⟦br⟧
